Author: roburst
Title: [ANN][Pre-Sale]ðŸ”¥ðŸ”¥ Roburst Network - The next-gen cashless payment ðŸ”¥ðŸ”¥-AIRDROP
Body: Thank you for your compliment!  We do not state the previous event because our team's principle is to look at the future. That's why we never want to put our past to the roadmap (actually we can say that this idea may come back to 2008 and no one could verify it).  Also, as we stated, our mobile, desktop wallet applications will be available when the main net launches. If you want to become a delegate in Roburst Network (just like miner, forging blocks to earn rewards), you have to wait after we finish testing on the test net.  The trading platform is being developed and will be available for beta testing in April. But I would say that the applications of our product is not limited at this trading platform. We use the trading platform as a demo for people to see the ability of our product.  If you want to know more about us, you can join our Telegram group discussion. We have technical guys there who could answer deeper about technical things.
